msgstr "本指南介绍如何为 NotebookLM 编写和运行测试。"

#: ../../development/testing.md:5 826440b5f3874f0fb100bfa4b327698a
msgid "Test Framework"
msgstr "测试框架"

#: ../../development/testing.md:7 b8d96105ea1845c4b1301c5b387cdfa7
msgid ""
"NotebookLM uses [Vitest](https://vitest.dev/) (v4+) as its test "
"framework, configured in `vitest.config.ts`."
msgstr ""
"NotebookLM 使用 [Vitest](https://vitest.dev/)（v4+）作为测试框架，配置在 "
"`vitest.config.ts` 中。"

