msgid "Test File Location"
msgstr "测试文件位置"

#: ../../development/testing.md:52 904e153ffe504bd884512705502acdea
msgid "Test files should be co-located with the source files they test:"
msgstr "测试文件应与它们测试的源文件放在一起："

